snippet: Shares on Wall Street ended higher, led by the technology sector.
abstract: Stocks rise on Wall Street, led by gains in technology companies and pushing the Standard & Poor's 500-stock index to its highest level since Election Day.
lead_paragraph: Shares on Wall Street ended higher, led by the technology sector.
